com.gensym.net.g2
Class G2Connection

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--java.net.URLConnection
        |
        +--com.gensym.net.g2.G2Connection
public class G2Connection
extends URLConnection

This class is a representation of an open connection to a G2 as a result of opening a URL. It can be used to resolve the URL and download its contents. This might not suppport all the generic methods that can be called. (Mostly throws exceptions for getting the InputStream, bytes, or ContentHeaders). The latter might actually be supported if we can actually determine the type of the item that can be retreived as an RPC call.
